sample.MainProxy

type
class
extends
primevc.mvc.Proxy<primevc.core.Bindable_String{ }>
MainProxy corresponds to a proxy in the MVC model. It retrieves data and passes it to the model. In this example MainProxy is the only proxy. It retrieves a single piece of data which is the URL of the image to be loaded.
